    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer48353560" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10052550272215076713">This compilation of &quot;greatest hits&quot; from Darrow&apos;s trials is a great read. Darrow&apos;s eloquence is extraordinary. Many classic moments are here: Darrow&apos;s cross-examination of William Jennings Bryan in the Scopes trial (some of which was lifted, almost verbatim, in &quot;Inherit the Wind&quot;); Darrow&apos;s plea for the lives of Leopold and Loeb during their infamous murder trial and much more. <br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText10052550272215076713" style="display:none">This compilation of "greatest hits" from Darrow's trials is a great read. Darrow's eloquence is extraordinary. Many classic moments are here: Darrow's cross-examination of William Jennings Bryan in the Scopes trial (some of which was lifted, almost verbatim, in "Inherit the Wind"); Darrow's plea for the lives of Leopold and Loeb during their infamous murder trial and much more. <br /><br /></span>
